(135, 1, '2018-11-02 13:54:47', '2018-11-02 13:54:47', '<h2>About</h2>\r\nVanish detergent liquid is ideal for delivering unbeatable stain removal efficacy that no other ordinary detergent alone can deliver. Its quick action formula removes the most toughest of stains and marks that dont go away easily and leaves your clothes looking fresh as new.\r\n| Removes the toughest of stains that no washing powder alone can remove.\r\n| Whitens your whites and brightens your coloured garments with its active brighteners\r\n| Use Vanish easily with both hand wash and machine wash, both direct and diluted. Add Vanish along with your detergent and get dry-clean like results for your everyday clothes in every wash.\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Use</strong>\r\n\r\nHand Wash -Apply some Vanish Liquid directly on the stained area of the cloth.Add 60 ml of Vanish liquid along with the detergent in half a bucket of water.Soak the stained cloth in the bucket (6 hours for whites and 1 hour for colored clothes).Wash as usual and rinse thoroughly.Machine Wash -Apply some Vanish Liquid directly on the stained area of the cloth.Add Vanish liquid along with the detergent.Wash as usual.\r\n\r\n<u></u>', 'Vanish Liquid - Expert Stain Removal Laundry Additive, 800 ml Can', 'Add Vanish along with your detergent and get dry-clean like results for your everyday clothes in every wash.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'vanish-liquid-expert-stain-removal-laundry-additive-800-ml-can', '', '', '2020-05-31 15:59:03', '2020-05-31 15:59:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/printer-shop/?post_type=product&#038;p=135', 0, 'product', '', 0),
