(213, 1, '2018-11-03 08:55:53', '2018-11-03 08:55:53', '<h2>About the Product</h2>\r\nMuesli works well as a whole grain breakfast cereal. With delicious, crunchy clusters of quinoas, oats, brown rice, nutrient dense flax and chia seeds and antioxidant and omega-3 rich dark chocolate and cranberry, Dark Chocolate + Cranberry muesli will kickstart your mornings and unlock the power of your day. Owing to the ingredients chosen, it has a definitive nutritive value.\r\n\r\n<strong>Ingredients</strong>\r\n\r\nWhole Grains (Rolled Oats 26%, Brown Rice Flakes 24%), Seeds (Quinoa 8%, Pumpkin, Chia 2%, Flax 2%), Dried Fruits (Raisins, Dried Cranberries 5%), Belgian Dark Chocolate 12% (Cocoa, Cocoa Butter, Sugar, Soy, Lecithin), Date Syrup, Almonds 4%, Soy Protein Flakes, Jaggery, Rice Bran Oil, Cocoa Powder, Himalayan Pink Salt.\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Use</strong>\r\n\r\nJust add the muesli to your bowl of milk. Pour some milk of your choice. Milk can also be replaced with yoghurt, cream or as a topping for desserts. You can also enjoy the taste as it is.', 'Yoga bar Muesli - Dark Chocolate & Cranberry, 400 g', 'Owing to the ingredients chosen, it has a definitive nutritive value.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'yoga-bar-muesli-dark-chocolate-cranberry-400-g', '', '', '2020-05-31 09:56:19', '2020-05-31 09:56:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/printer-shop/?post_type=product&#038;p=213', 0, 'product', '', 0),
