(219, 1, '2018-11-03 09:06:10', '2018-11-03 09:06:10', '<h2>About the Product</h2>\r\nMcCain Smiles are delicious mashed potatoes, seasoned and shaped into happy faces. Best enjoyed with Tomato Mayonnaise dip. Go ahead, take a bite and keep smiling!\r\n\r\n<strong>Nutritional Facts</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Energy- 209.27 Kcal Total Fat- 8.31 g Saturated Fatty Acids- 3.93 g Monounsaturated Fatty Acids- 2.15 g Polyunsaturated Fatty Acids- 2.23 g Trans Fatty Acids- 0 g Protein- 4.72 g Total Carbohydrate- 28.90 g Sugar- 0.32 g Cholesterol- 0 mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>How to Use</strong>\r\n\r\nStep 1 Preheat the oil in Kadhai/Wok (max temperature upto 175 c), Step 2 Take the product from the freezer, Fry Directly Do not Thaw, Step 3 Put the desired quantity gently in hot oil and deep fry for 3 minutes, Step 4 Seal &amp; Keep the remaining product in freezer.\r\n\r\n<u></u>', 'McCain Smiles Crispy - Happy Potatoes, 1.25 kg', 'McCain Smiles are delicious mashed potatoes, seasoned and shaped into happy faces. Best enjoyed with Tomato Mayonnaise dip.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mccain-smiles-crispy-happy-potatoes-1-25-kg', '', '', '2020-05-31 15:12:49', '2020-05-31 15:12:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/printer-shop/?post_type=product&#038;p=219', 0, 'product', '', 0),
