(230, 1, '2018-11-03 09:50:58', '2018-11-03 09:50:58', '<h2>About the Product</h2>\r\nWhiskas Kitten Gravy Food provides complete nutrition for your pet kitten. A complete and balanced cat food, Whiskas gravy is designed to take care of your pets daily nutritional requirements and provide it with all the required vitamins and minerals along with moisture and nourishment for healthy growth and happy life. A cat\'s love for fish is thoughtfully blended with loads of calcium, phosphorus, proteins, antioxidants, vitamins &amp; minerals, in each pack. It helps maintain its fur and provides it with healthy bones and body growth, healthy immune system, and energy for play. Whiskas gravy has a texture and aroma that appeals to the palate of your feline, and attracts even fussy eaters in for a filling and fun mealtime!\r\n\r\nWhiskas cat food is ideal for kitten breeds from Persian Cat, British Shorthair to Siamese Cat.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Feeding Instructions</strong>\r\n\r\nEnsure your cat gets a complete, balanced meal by feeding its daily nutritional requirement as follows:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Morning: 1 pouch</li>\r\n 	<li>In-Between: 15g of dry food</li>\r\n 	<li>Evening: 1 pouch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Note:</strong>This is for pet cats that have their main sustenance diet through home-prepared or dry cat food.\r\n\r\nRefer to the back of the pack for complete instructions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Ingredients</strong>\r\n\r\nWholegrain Cereals (Corn, Rice, Wheat), Corn Gluten Meal, Poultry &amp; Poultry By-products, Soy Bean Products (Full-Fat Soy Bean, Soy Bean Meal), Palm Stearin, Tuna Fish, Wheat Flour, Minerals, Iodised Salt, Vitamins, Taurine, Soy Oil, Methionine, Food Colouring |Preservatives, Flavour.', 'Whiskas Wet Cat Food - Tuna In Jelly, For Kittens, 2-12 Months, 85 g (Pack of 6)', 'Whiskas gravy has a texture and aroma that appeals to the palate of your feline, and attracts even fussy eaters in for a filling and fun mealtime!', 'publish', 'open