(234, 1, '2018-11-03 09:55:21', '2018-11-03 09:55:21', '<h2><strong>Overview</strong></h2>\r\nDettol is one of the world\'s most trusted antiseptic protection brands which gives you 99.99% protection against disease-causing bacteria and germs. Their liquid handwash protects you from 100 illness-causing germs. This multi-purpose liquid is ideal for personal and home hygiene. It provides expert protection against harmful bacteria with a unique sanitizing formula and takes care of you and your family from harmful germs. It is also known to be safe for use on skin.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Use Dettol liquid handwash to protect the transference of germs from your hands.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dermatologically tested. Provides 10 times better protection vs ordinary handwash soaps.</li>\r\n 	<li>With original Dettol protection, it helps keep your hands hygienically clean and refreshed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Recommended by the Indian Medical Association.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Composition</strong>\r\n\r\nAqua, Elaeis Guineensis (palm) Kemel Oil, Potassium Hydroxide, Glycol Stearate, Cocamide Mea, Palm Stearin Fatty Acid, Potassium Chloride, Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Pinus Palustris Oil, Preservatives, Sodium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Disodium Edta, Zinc Stearate, Etidronic Acid, Isopropyl Alcohol, Parfum, Ci 11710, Ci 12085, P-chloro-m-cresol.\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Use</strong>\r\n\r\nWet hands with clean water. Apply a small amount of soap. Rub your hands together until bubbly. Once done, rinse with water and dry.', 'Dettol Hand Wash Liquid Refill - Original, 175 ml', 'Dettol is one of the world\'s most trusted antiseptic protection brand which gives you 99.99% protection against disease-causing bacteria and germs.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dettol-hand-wash-liquid-refill-original-175-ml', '', '', '2020-05-29 06:09:19', '2020-05-29 06:09:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/printer-shop/?post_type=product&#038;p=234', 0, 'product', '', 0),
