(395, 1, '2018-11-13 10:52:58', '2018-11-13 10:52:58', '<a href=\"http://localhost/printer-shop/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/about-us.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/printer-shop/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/about-us-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone img-align size-medium wp-image-324\" /></a><p>Based in Somerset, NJ we have been supplying high quality printers &amp; parts for over years. Whether you work from home or have a fortune 500 company we are more than capable of providing you with all your imaging needs. GlobtierNxt is a leading printer seller of refurbished, commercial laser printers, wide format printers, office jet printer etc. Check our site for Printers on sale, color laser printer sales and deals.</p><p>GlobtierNxt offers a complete line of used HP, Cannon, Brother Printers, refurbished printers, used laser / Photo printer for sale, refurbished office printers, used HP printers for sale and multifunctional devices from all brands. After sale support is a priority for us. Contact us directly and we can help. We offer competitive pricing backed by outstanding customer service and technical support, both before and after the sale.</p><p>GlobtierNxt is a group of highly skilled and friendly printer technicians located in Somerset, New Jersey. What makes us unique in our industry is our obsession with quality. I know, EVERYONE claims to have great quality, but in our years of observing this industry, very few companies really take quality seriously. As a technician its frustrating to see the proliferation of cheap, low quality parts and after sales service. Weve had customers telling about their purchasing departments thought they were saving money by buying the cheapest services and parts they could find, when in fact they were losing money because they had to replace them almost twice as often! In the long run, quality services and parts will save you more time and money through longer product lives and fewer service calls.</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '52-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-13 10:52:58', '2018-11-13 10:52:58', '', 52, 'http://localhost/printer-shop/2018/11/13/52-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(397, 1, '2018-11-13 11:20:09', '2018-11-13 11:20:09', '<img src=\"http://localhost/printer-shop/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/printers-1-300x100.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-352\" /><h5>Printer Repair Service</h5><p>GlobtierNxt is an independent printer repair service provider of third party Printer products and has no affiliation with any third party brand and any of their product or service offerings.</p><p>Our printer repair service organizations specializing in most major brands of laser printers, color printers, multifunctional printers, laserjet printers, inkjet printers, dot matrix printers, serial matrix printers, continuous form, line matrix printers, impact printers, RFID printers, portable printers, barcode printers. Mobile printers, direct thermal printers, thermal transfer printers, PAX print engines and printer applicators.</p><p>With a <strong>Technical Assistance Center at 1-844-505-5014</strong> printer repair support is available. GlobtierNxt highly trained and experienced support personnel are available to meet your printer repair needs.</p><h5>We offer service:</h5><ul class=\"list-pages\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"><li>Complete printer solution for all brands new and old printers.</li><li>Resolve every printer related issues- Printer Installation &amp; Setup, Printer Offline, Printer Driver Outdated issues, Page alignment issues, Ink or Ink Cartridge issues, Fax issues, Printer Scanner issues and all other major and minor printer issues.</li><li>Printer support service for anyone, anywhere and anytime.</li><li>Phone Support, Chat Support for Printer Problems.</li><li>No hidden or extra charges. We take genuine technician charges for resolving issues.</li><li>Resolve Printer Scanner &amp; Fax complicated issues.</li><li>Onsite printer repair service at affordable cost.</li></ul><h5>Printer Repair Service Plan</h5><div class=\"section group bdr\"><div class=\"section group\"><div class=\"col 