(546, 1, '2019-12-02 12:27:14', '2019-12-02 12:27:14', '<a href=\"http://localhost/printer-shop/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/about-us.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone img-align size-medium wp-image-324\" src=\"http://localhost/printer-shop/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/about-us-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" /></a>IFaa Store is among the USAs leading electronic device retailers, operating online stores and physical warehouses nationwide. Founded in 2018, in Maryland, IFaa Store is growing progressively. Our high-volume warehouses and online stores are designed to satisfy the need for worldwide customers. We fulfill the technical requirement of our customers in case of their need, by providing them, well-trained associates. Based in Ellicott, Maryland we have been supplying electronic gadget and GPS devices for over years. Whether you work from home or have a fortune 500 company we are more than capable of providing you with all your imaging needs. IFaa Store is a leading electronic gadget and GPS device etc. Check our site for electronic gadget and GPS device sales and deals.\r\n\r\nIFaa Store offers a complete line of used Smartwatch ,Cables ,GPS Navigation and Accessories, Streaming Media Player,Slider Product and multifunctional devices from all brands. After sale support is a priority for us. Contact us directly and we can help. We offer competitive pricing backed by outstanding customer service before and after the sale.\r\n\r\nIFaa Store is a group of highly skilled and friendly electronic gadget and GPS device technicians located in Ellicott, Maryland. What makes us unique in our industry is our obsession with quality. I know, EVERYONE claims to have great quality, but in our years of observing this industry, very few companies really take quality seriously. As a technician its frustrating to see the proliferation of cheap, low quality parts and after sales service. Weve had customers telling about their purchasing departments thought they were saving money by buying the cheapest services and parts they could find, when in fact they were losing money because they had to replace them almost twice as often! In the long run, quality services and parts will save you more time and money through longer product lives and fewer service calls.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '52-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-02 12:27:14', '2019-12-02 12:27:14', '', 52, 'http://ifaastore.com/2019/12/02/52-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
